vim bazel-out/host/bin/external/io_bazel_rules_closure/closure/private/gensrcjar +69. After it,adding next sentences can fix upwards error.

export PROTO_COMPILER = /path/to/protoc
export GRPC_JAVA_PLUGIN = /path/to/protoc-gen-grpc-java

Then i get a new error Executing genrule //tensorflow/tensorboard/components/tf_tensorboard:ts failed: bash failed: error executing command
How should i do next?
